-- Spain's Bankia sells 19 pct stake in Metrovacesa to Santander-source
-- By Carlos Ruano
-- Thu Dec 04, 2014 05:55AM EST
-- None



MADRID, Dec 4 (Reuters) - Spanish nationalised bank Bankia <BKIA.MC> has sold its 19.07 percent stake in property firm Metrovacesa to the country's largest bank Santander <SAN.MC>, a source close to the operation said on Thursday.

